    "en": {
      "title": "34 who left the country are caught in the middle of the sea",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Police Media Spokesman, Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Lduwa, 34 persons who were traveling in two multi-day vessels to illegally migrate to a foreign country have been arrested by the officers of Trincomalee, Navy Base in Valachchena and Kuchchaveli sea limits.",
        "The media spokesperson said that there were two women and two children among that group.",
        "The suspects will be produced before the Trincomalee Magistrate's Court today."
      ],
